Implemented new user notification system. Added email and in-app notifications using SendGrid API and WebSocket connections. Created notification preferences UI where users can configure what they want to be notified about.

```typescript
interface NotificationPreference {
  email: boolean;
  inApp: boolean;
  types: ('mention' | 'reply' | 'like')[];
}

async function sendNotification(
  userId: string,
  type: NotificationType,
  content: string
) {
  const prefs = await getPreferences(userId);

  if (prefs.email && prefs.types.includes(type)) {
    await emailService.send(userId, content);
  }

  if (prefs.inApp) {
    await wsService.notify(userId, { type, content });
  }
}
```
